ic winds) in the halos of more actively\nstar-forming galaxies dominate the absorption-cross section of strong MgII\nabsorbers in the local Universe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Jan 2013 21:00:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
