5 GHz, important non-Gaussian deviations in\nCMB anisotropy maps are expected due to unresolved extragalactic sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jan 2013 14:28:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Mar 2013 18:29:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
